Plot: Psychologist Nestor Bukowski wants to forget the past and be with his new girlfriend. Unfortunately, he can't. The question of what happened to Edita still haunts him, so he decides to investigate it by himself, no matter the cost.
Title: Cirkus Bukowsky
Actors: Pavel Reznícek, Hynek Cermák, Predrag Bjelac, Marika Soposká
